{"tid":1120963,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動畫公司Ufotable  遭控挪用日本311震災捐款","createTime":"2019-04-23T04:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T08:48:49.000Z","uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9296941be484d1fcb0e80223cdf65b8a1cbaf7a9","tid":1120963,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"HF3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《Fate》動畫公司遭控挪用東日本震災捐款，《鬼滅之刃》製作恐受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019-04-12 22:00&nbsp;By 餅乾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n日本動畫公司 ufotable 今年初才推出動畫劇場版《Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] II.迷途之蝶》，就被週刊文春爆料涉嫌假造帳目及逃漏稅。今（12）日被指出其逃漏稅金額達 4 億日圓，其假造帳目當中還包含東日本大震災的慈善義賣收入。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n根據日本國稅局的調查， ufotable 的周邊收入並非轉入公司帳戶，而是由社長近藤光以現金方式收取。其中逃漏稅金額可能高達 4 億日圓，以及約 2 億日圓的追徵稅款。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n另外，週刊記者在向東京國稅局取材訪問時，被回以「我們無法回答個別案件內容」，只是根據當局消息人士透露，近藤社長似乎承認當局所提出的指控。目前週刊文春未能收到近藤社長本人的答覆。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n週刊文春更指出，ufotable 自 2011 年 10 月為 311 東日本大震災舉辦的慈善義賣會「マチ★アソビ」（machi asobi）的收入也與實際帳目不符，可能是遭到相關人員不當挪用。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n「ufotable 未依法律規定謊報實際收益，已違反法人稅法」律師小林利明表示，「另外，以慈善活動為名義獲取不當利益，此行為更觸犯刑法 246 條詐欺罪，最高可處十年以下有期徒刑。」<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nufotable 製作的電視動畫《鬼滅之刃》甫播出第一集，另一方面《Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel]》第三集也還在籌備中，這些作品可能會因為 ufotable 接連不斷的財務醜聞而產生變數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38531/ufotable-suspected-to-evade-taxes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F38531%2Fufotable-suspected-to-evade-taxes&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=e619a795\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38531/ufotable-suspected-to-evade-taxes</a>"},{"pid":"5917de2b642d1d1433391faee520ca8826ffef61","tid":1120963,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef3db79243697ff2d9997f81c4140cb663cb130","tid":1120963,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"一定又係支那人搞鬼"},{"pid":"fe57bd52aabf9f3118967a52a7e8a0fc523343d9","tid":1120963,"uid":201823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"前幾日先話鬼滅之刃二季26話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca80e495ec88f060b368363032108299e96998c","tid":1120963,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b9c840ebd09e9f6fe33eb9239cefddc44cf98ed","tid":1120963,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"ff末落"},{"pid":"8e81da3f30d09b34e0c80597f76bd6f26353d65b","tid":1120963,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca80e495ec88f060b368363032108299e96998c","tid":1120963,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"唔污糟係入唔到佢哋個圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為唔造呢d嘢的異類，會威脅到呢群既得利益者。"},{"pid":"74b2b7d5f3e12ee041cdb03fece6c1bfa82724a3","tid":1120963,"uid":137731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c72cd5b36addb50b234c1e6540cacc8edff4f247","tid":1120963,"uid":22949,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"執柒等A1接手吧<br />\n睇過刀劍都知A1世界第一"},{"pid":"be8170136c33a90f8252e64ff32fddbb70db360f","tid":1120963,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72cd5b36addb50b234c1e6540cacc8edff4f247","tid":1120963,"uid":22949,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"執柒等A1接手吧<br />\n睇過刀劍都知A1世界第一"},"citedBy":0,"re